      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy verification for hemolysis transport equation using manufactured solution; convergence rate within 10% of theoretical order.",
      "rationale": "Method of manufactured solutions applied to simplified 2-D channel hemolysis transport; observed order 1.87 vs theoretical 2.0 (6.5% deviation). Full 3-D rotating frame MMS not completed. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
