      "rationale": "Iterative residuals reported at 1e-5 level only; mass imbalance not quantified in submitted documentation. Floating-point accumulation error in hemolysis scalar not assessed. Factor flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 3."
    },
