      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification of turbulence model selection for rotating blood pump flows; hemolysis constitutive model uncertainty quantified; sensitivity of NIH to model form choices documented.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on literature precedent but no systematic model-form sensitivity study conducted for this geometry. Hemolysis model coefficient uncertainty included in Monte Carlo but model-form uncertainty (e.g., linear vs power-law damage accumulation) not assessed. Achieved level 2 against required level 5."
    },
