      "acceptanceCriteria": "All uncertain input parameters identified; probability distributions assigned with traceability to measurement data or literature; correlation structure between inputs characterised.",
      "rationale": "Three input uncertainty sources identified and included in Monte Carlo. Correlation structure between inlet velocity profile and viscosity not characterised. Wall roughness and impeller clearance gap uncertainties not included. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
