      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental sample size sufficient for statistical characterisation of hemolysis variability; batch-to-batch variability in blood analogue documented; outlier analysis performed.",
      "rationale": "FDA pump dataset provides single-replicate measurements at each operating point. No batch-to-batch variability data available. Statistical characterisation of experimental hemolysis variability not possible with available data. Epistemic gap. Achieved level 1 against required level 3."
